{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ping-pong-club-retrospective-album/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ping Pong Club Tarik Perhatian Lewat Album Retrospective","content":"\n<p>Tahun 2019 nampaknya bakal jadi tahun yang sangat asyik buat penggemar indie pop Indonesia. Pasalnya, kemunculan band <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pingpongclub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Ping Pong Club (opens in a new tab)\">Ping Pong Club</a> membawa sebuah kesegaran dalam genre musik satu ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53367\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ping-pong-club-retrospective-album/attachment/02-ppc-retrospective/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ppc-retrospective\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" alt=\"Ping Pong Club. Sumber: Wasted Rockers\" class=\"wp-image-53367\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ppc-retrospective.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Ping Pong Club. Sumber: Wasted Rockers</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Band asal kota Bandung yang digawangi oleh Hariz Lasa (vokal/synth), Muhammad Rizky (vokal/gitar), Fasya Suryadini (vokal/keyboard), serta Satrio Adi Nugroho (drum) ini telah hadir sejak tahun 2017 silam. Semuanya dimulai berkat kesamaan antara Hariz dan Rizky yang sama-sama menyukai musik britpop, entah itu The Beatles hingga musisi generasi Sarah Records. Dengan tambahan personil Fasya dan Satrio, band <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pingpongclubtheband/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Ping Pong Club</a> pun dibentuk, dimana nama tersebut terinspirasi dari jargon efek ping pong dalam dunia audio.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sepanjang tahun 2018, Ping Pong Club sudah merilis tiga single: Venetian Blinds, Skylight, dan Ecstatic. Ketiganya mendapatkan respon hangat dari fans. Menjawab keinginan fans akan lebih banyak materi lagu Ping Pong Club, mereka merilis album Retrospective berisi 3 single terdahulu, 4 lagu baru, serta 2 remix track.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53370\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ping-pong-club-retrospective-album/attachment/05-ppc-retrospective/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-ppc-retrospective\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Retrospective, album perdana Ping Pong Club. Sumber: Ping Pong Club&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" alt=\"Retrospective, album perdana Ping Pong Club. Sumber: Ping Pong Club\" class=\"wp-image-53370\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ppc-retrospective.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Retrospective, album perdana Ping Pong Club. Sumber: Ping Pong Club</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Album ini memilik konsep &#8220;past, present, future&#8221; yang juga menjadi judul dari track pertama Retrospective. Tema tersebut direfleksikan lewat kemasan musik indie pop, new wave, serta sophisti-pop tahun 80-90an yang diterjemahkan ke dalam gaya yang lebih kekinian. Liriknya menceritakan pemahaman manusia akan cinta, konflik, pencarian jati diri, hingga kuasa yang lebih besar dari alam semesta.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53369\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ping-pong-club-retrospective-album/attachment/04-ppc-retrospective/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-ppc-retrospective\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" alt=\"Sajikan nuansa brit pop klasik dengan kemasan modern. Sumber: Emerging Indie Bands\" class=\"wp-image-53369\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ppc-retrospective.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sajikan nuansa brit pop klasik dengan kemasan modern. Sumber: Emerging Indie Bands</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Venetian Blinds, Skylight, dan Ecstatic menjadi tiga single yang hadir lebih dulu dalam album Retrospective. Mereka didampingi oleh empat lagu baru, yaitu Past, Present, Future; Retrospective; A Step Closer to Yout Room, dan She&#8217;s Your Trouble. Selain itu ada pula dua remix track yang digarap Muhammad Rizky, dan Muhammad Iqbal yang merupakan frontman band <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"ikkubaru (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ikkubaru-silent-single-terbaru/\" target=\"_blank\">ikkubaru</a> serta support bassist untuk Ping Pong Club.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/chit-chat-ikkubaru-dhira-bongs/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ikkubaru &amp; Dhira Bongs: Ciptakan Musik Hingga ke Jepang</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"1280\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1tso8wP0njM\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Lagu-lagu tersebut memiliki warna yang cerah serta ceria. Kombinasi permainan synth, ketukan drum, serta petikan gitar bergaya indie ini membuat lagu-lagu Ping Pong Club mudah dicerna dan diterima. Rolling vokalis antara Hariz, Rizky, dan Fasya, membuat lagu-lagu Ping Pong Club menonjol satu sama lain.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53368\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ping-pong-club-retrospective-album/attachment/03-ppc-retrospective/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-ppc-retrospective\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ppc-retrospective.jpg\" alt=\"Ping Pong Club tampilkan tiga vokalis dengan karakter berbeda. Sumber: Unite Asia\" class=\"wp-image-53368\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ppc-retrospective.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ppc-retrospective-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Ping Pong Club tampilkan tiga vokalis dengan karakter berbeda. Sumber: Unite Asia</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Album Retrospective dari Ping Pong Club telah rilis secara fisik pada tanggal 28 Februari lalu, disusul dengan versi digital pada tanggal 9 Maret 2019. Kamu bisa mendapatkan album fisik Retrospective di record store favorit kamu, dan untuk versi digital bisa didengarkan melalui <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Spotify (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/7sXHAFpGtSTIOZpXEghdBJ?si=i3np0dSbT2u-VDKhJQPoHg\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a> serta layanan musik favorit lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/7sXHAFpGtSTIOZpXEghdBJ\" width=\"300\" height=\"380\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allow=\"encrypted-media\"></iframe>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"d77f9a7c-2cf1-5610-98c3-80202b2b6e70"}}}